parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Sudden Loss of Power and Unintended Neutral
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden loss of power and unintended neutral can cause the vehicle to lose speed rapidly, increasing the risk of accidents, especially on high-speed roads.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly loses power
the transmission shifts into neutral
the dashboard displays multiple warning lights
the vehicle's speed is reduced rapidly
the vehicle becomes difficult to control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The high voltage battery malfunction can cause the vehicle to lose power, reducing its range and increasing the risk of accidents, especially on high-speed roads.

the vehicle displays warning messages
the vehicle is unable to start
the battery modules have bloated cells due to overheating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The traction motor inverter failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, reducing its range and increasing the risk of accidents, especially on high-speed roads.

the vehicle displays warning messages

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The airbag and seatbelt warning lights can indicate a malfunction in the safety system, increasing the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The protective safe mode engagement can cause the vehicle to lose power and speed, increasing the risk of accidents, especially on high-speed roads.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Erratic Battery Mileage and AEB Malfunction
